      <h6>The Tool of Data-Based Personas</h6>
      <p>With user research, I learned that for journalists a medical conference can make for a challenging day. From synthesizing the interview responses into personas with bios, goals, frustrations, and motiviations, I now had an impactful tool to inform the following user testing:
