      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-lg-6 aha-conclusions">
        <h6>The Card Sort Takeaways</h6>
        <p>The medical journalists would want an organization in the site that would streamline their access to maps, schedules, interview times, research, contacts, and surveys.</p>
        <p>The card sort insight would inform the best scenarios to test using the Morae usability software.</p>
